      <item>
        <title>Half-Life: Alyx (Valve VR game)</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Chickenprotector]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Mm. Happy for a new installment, but on the fence because no VR set for me yet, the tech isn’t where I want it to be to get a cheap one.</p>
<p>I’m more interested in the tech demo they’ve got. '07 is when we got EP 2, so it’s been 12 years since we got a half-life game if you ignore the little updates they’ve done to the engine(s) here and there, and nothing really concrete to showcase the new engine, and uses Source 2 to its fullest.</p>
<p>This game will prolly show a lot of what they’ve really been doing to the engine for the past decade.</p>
